OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showery rain and
OL,6,Fthunderstorms clearing northeastwards
OL,7,Fto leave a largely dry day, with
OL,8,Fprolonged spells of hazy sunshine.
OL,9,FBecoming exceptionally hot, markedly
OL,10,Fhotter than Thursday, especially in
OL,11,Feastern areas. Chance of isolated
OL,12,Fthunderstorm late in the day. Feeling
OL,13,Fhumid.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FAn exceptionally hot end to
OL,16,Fthe day, with perhaps the chance of a
OL,17,Ffew thunderstorms during the evening.
OL,18,FStaying largely dry with clear spells
OL,19,Fovernight. Another warm and humid
OL,20,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
