OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry with variable
OL,6,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,7,FChance of heavy showers and
OL,8,Fthunderstorms arriving from the south
OL,9,Fduring the evening. Still feeling very
OL,10,Fwarm and humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBands
OL,13,Fof showers, heavy and possibly
OL,14,Fthundery, moving east Sunday,
OL,15,Fintroducing much fresher conditions.
OL,16,FDry with warm sunny spells Monday.
OL,17,FScattered, occasionally heavy, showers
OL,18,Fon Tuesday. Temperatures nearer normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
